cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CL 

The paper deals with a large-scale video classification dataset and the use of machine learning techniques for classification. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Other likely sub-categories include cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.CL (Computation and Language) as the paper also deals with natural language processing techniques for labeling the videos.
